org.openlca.core.results

Class CostResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openlca.core.results.CostResult

  • public class CostResult
extends Object
    Represents the result of LCC calculation. Note that the fix-cost and variable-cost indices and results can be null. You can use the CostResults class to generate results for the views.
